text: The Black Forest Girl () is a 1950 German romantic drama movie directed by Hans Deppe and based on the 1917 play of the same name by Leon Jessel and August Neidhart. It stars Paul Hörbiger, Sonja Ziemann, Gretl Schörg, Rudolf Prack, Walter Müller, Ernst Waldow. ==Other websites== * Category:1950 romantic drama movies Category:German drama movies
title: The Black Forest Girl (1950 movie)
